balanceOf(address).details: Returns the number of NFTs in `owner`'s account. ERC721 related function.

childIdOf(uint256,string).details: Provides child token (subdomain) of provided tokenId. Registry related function.

params.label: label of subdomain (for `aaa.bbb.crypto` it will be `aaa`)

exists(uint256).details: Returns whether token exists or not.

isApprovedOrOwner(address,uint256).details: Returns whether the given spender can transfer a given token ID. Registry related function.

params.spender: address of the spender to query
params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to be transferred

returns._0: bool whether the msg.sender is approved for the given token ID, is an operator of the owner, or is the owner of the token

ownerOf(uint256).details: Returns the owner of the NFT specified by `tokenId`. ERC721 related function.

resolverOf(uint256).details: Gets the resolver of the specified token ID. Registry related function.

params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to query the resolver of

returns._0: address currently marked as the resolver of the given token ID
